fields.name: Icmp
fields.description: Pinhole timeout for ICMP pinholes in seconds. Default for ICMP Echo is 30 seconds.

fields.name: Tcp
fields.description: Pinhole timeout for TCP pinholes in seconds. Default for TCP is 3 minutes.

fields.name: Udp
fields.description: Pinhole timeout for UDP pinholes in seconds. Default for UDP is 30 seconds.
